I've created the Text feature developer guide at `docs/generated/text.md`. The document covers:

- **Text Style Objects**: Underline, Shadow, Outline, LineThrough, and Bevel styles with fluent API examples
- **Input Filtering**: InputFilter with allow/deny patterns using regex
- **Text Fit Configuration**: FitRange and FitCandidate for automatic font sizing
- **Font Variation Axes**: FontVariationAxis for OpenType variable font control

All API usage has been verified against the public headers in `repos/dali-ui/dali-ui-foundation/public-api/text/`. The examples are adapted from actual sample files in the repository.
